                        {
                            "id": "57dee07",
                            "settings": {
                                "editor": "<p>We are looking for a talented and detail-oriented UI Designer to join our growing team. The ideal candidate has a strong visual design sense, deep understanding of modern interface patterns, and the ability to create clean, user-focused designs for web applications, SaaS platforms, and marketing websites. You will work closely with product managers, developers, and stakeholders to design intuitive and visually engaging user interfaces.<\/p>"
                            },
                            "widgetType": "text-editor",
                            "elType": "widget"
                        }
                    ],
                    "elType": "container",
                    "isInner": true
                },
                {
                    "id": "0e596d4",
                    "settings": {
                        "content_width": "full",
                        "ma_el_slider_delay": "5000"
                    },
                    "elements": [
                        {
                            "id": "1b051fb",
                            "settings": {
                                "title": "Key Responsibilities",
                                "header_size": "h5"
                            },
                            "widgetType": "heading",
                            "elType": "widget"
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "bf72d6a",
                            "settings": {
                                "editor": "<ul><li>Design modern, clean, and user-friendly interfaces for websites, dashboards, and web applications<\/li><li>Create wireframes, mockups, and high-fidelity UI designs using Figma<\/li><li>Develop and maintain reusable UI components and design systems<\/li><li>Ensure consistent visual styles across all products and platforms<\/li><li>Design responsive layouts for desktop, tablet, and mobile devices<\/li><li>Collaborate with developers to ensure accurate implementation of designs<\/li><li>Improve existing interfaces based on feedback and usability best practices<\/li><li>Stay updated with the latest UI trends, tools, and design standards<\/li><\/ul>"
                            },
                            "widgetType": "text-editor",
                            "elType": "widget"
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "18ea011",
                            "settings": {
                                "title": "Required Skills and Qualifications",
                                "header_size": "h5"
                            },
                            "widgetType": "heading",
                            "elType": "widget"
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "f75c153",
                            "settings": {
                                "editor": "<ul><li>Strong proficiency in Figma (Auto Layout, Components, Variants, Design Systems)<\/li><li>Solid understanding of typography, color theory, layout, and visual hierarchy<\/li><li>Experience designing modern websites, SaaS dashboards, or web applications<\/li><li>Strong knowledge of responsive design principles<\/li><li>Ability to create clean, organized, and developer-friendly design files<\/li><li>Understanding of UI\/UX best practices and usability principles<\/li><li>Strong attention to detail and consistency<\/li><\/ul>"
                            },
                            "widgetType": "text-editor",
                            "elType": "widget"
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "dad407e",
                            "settings": {
                                "title": "Preferred (Bonus) Skills",
                                "header_size": "h5"
                            },
                            "widgetType": "heading",
                            "elType": "widget"
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "8886ed0",
                            "settings": {
                                "editor": "<ul><li>Basic knowledge of HTML and CSS<\/li><li>Experience working with design systems<\/li><li>Experience designing admin dashboards or SaaS products<\/li><li>Familiarity with modern UI trends and interaction design<\/li><li>Experience working with developers in real projects<\/li><\/ul>"
                            },
                            "widgetType": "text-editor",
                            "elType": "widget"
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "8825c62",
                            "settings": {
                                "title": "What We Offer",
                                "header_size": "h5"
                            },
                            "widgetType": "heading",
                            "elType": "widget"
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "5687413",
                            "settings": {
                                "editor": "<ul><li>Opportunity to work on modern SaaS and web products<\/li><li>Collaborative and creative work environment<\/li><li>Long-term growth opportunity<\/li><li>Flexible working environment<\/li><li>Competitive salary based on experience and skill<\/li><\/ul>"
                            },
                            "widgetType": "text-editor",
                            "elType": "widget"
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "0841327",
                            "settings": {
                                "title": "Who Should Apply",
                                "header_size": "h5"
                            },
                            "widgetType": "heading",
                            "elType": "widget"
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "e0ffea6",
                            "settings": {
                                "editor": "<p>You are a great fit if you:<\/p><ul><li>Have a strong passion for UI design<\/li><li>Pay attention to small details<\/li><li>Can create modern, professional interfaces<\/li><li>Are willing to learn and improve continuously<\/li><\/ul>"
                            },
                            "widgetType": "text-editor",
                            "elType": "widget"
                        }
                    ],
                    "elType": "container",
                    "isInner": true
                },
                {
                    "id": "83711fa",
                    "settings": {
